862
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:55,360
Sophomore year,

863
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:57,080
I was adamant about getting married.

864
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:57,920
Senior year,

865
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,240
I got pregnant.

866
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:00,920
Then I dropped out to have a baby.

867
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,560
Then your kid must be big now.

868
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:05,760
12 years old.

869
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,920
I couldn't even tell

870
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,080
that you're also a mom.

871
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:11,000
What does your husband do?

872
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,320
Nothing.

873
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,840
He just idles around.

874
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:15,280
And you're not fighting with him?

875
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:17,640
Well,

876
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:19,480
we got divorced.

877
00:42:21,640 --> 00:42:23,360
That's too much information.

878
00:42:23,560 --> 00:42:25,200
I think we were never prepared

879
00:42:25,200 --> 00:42:26,360
to get married in the first place,

880
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:28,160
let alone become parents.

881
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:31,600
Tell you what, ever since I married into his family,

882
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:33,080
things have been weird.

883
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:35,080
His mother was so on guard against me.

884
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,680
She'd tell people

885
00:42:36,680 --> 00:42:38,800
that I got pregnant so that I could keep her son.

886
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:41,160
Since I wasn't originally from here,

887
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:43,760
she thought I was looking for a patron
 to stay in the big city.

888
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:45,040
I had argued with her

889
00:42:45,080 --> 00:42:46,560
over this several times.

890
00:42:46,560 --> 00:42:47,920
But not once did Shi Daming...

891
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:49,600
Shi Daming is my ex.

892
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,200
Not once was he on my side.

893
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:52,160
Why?

894
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:55,360
Because his mother is in charge of

895
00:42:55,360 --> 00:42:56,560
the family fortune.

896
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:59,240
He has to ask her for every cent he's spending.

897
00:43:00,360 --> 00:43:01,400
Then,

898
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:02,920
after our child was born,

899
00:43:02,920 --> 00:43:05,040
I put up with him for two more years.

900
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:07,440
We even had to ask his mother

901
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:09,360
for money to buy baby formula.

902
00:43:10,520 --> 00:43:12,200
I couldn't live like that anymore.

903
00:43:12,200 --> 00:43:13,440
So, I filed for divorce.

904
00:43:13,880 --> 00:43:15,160
And he agreed to it?

905
00:43:15,560 --> 00:43:16,240
He didn't,

906
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:18,200
but his mother did.

907
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:19,960
Because back then,

908
00:43:19,960 --> 00:43:21,800
his mother wanted to set him up with this girl

909
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:23,640
who is the daughter of her boss.

910
00:43:24,040 --> 00:43:25,680
She saw the divorce

911
00:43:26,680 --> 00:43:27,880
as an opportunity.

912
00:43:27,880 --> 00:43:29,680
So, she said to me,

913
00:43:30,040 --> 00:43:31,480
"Shanshan,

914
00:43:31,960 --> 00:43:34,360
you two are not meant for each other.

915
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,560
You're too good for my son."

916
00:43:37,120 --> 00:43:38,320
She's unbelievable.

917
00:43:38,320 --> 00:43:40,120
She asked her son to give me a sum of money.

918
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,720
I didn't take it.

919
00:43:42,680 --> 00:43:44,680
Are you still in touch with each other?

920
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:45,680
Yes.

921
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:47,640
I used to take my son to travel

922
00:43:47,640 --> 00:43:49,120
when I had time.

923
00:43:49,120 --> 00:43:51,120
I'm now planning to send my son abroad.

924
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:54,120
Do you hate his mother?

925
00:43:54,640 --> 00:43:55,640
There was a time

926
00:43:55,640 --> 00:43:57,280
when I would gnash my teeth

927
00:43:57,280 --> 00:43:58,720
even mentioning her.

928
00:44:00,560 --> 00:44:01,640
But later on,

929
00:44:01,640 --> 00:44:02,920
I learned something about her

930
00:44:04,360 --> 00:44:05,080
and my hatred went away.

931
00:44:06,040 --> 00:44:08,280
What about her that caused this 180-degree change?

932
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:14,560
I have a friend who's a nurse.

933
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:16,640
I had my baby

934
00:44:16,640 --> 00:44:18,280
in her hospital.

935
00:44:19,120 --> 00:44:22,240
She said that I was having a heart failure
 caused by obstructed labor.

936
00:44:22,720 --> 00:44:23,840
They asked a family member to sign a paper

937
00:44:23,840 --> 00:44:25,960
and decide who to save if anything happened.

938
00:44:25,960 --> 00:44:28,120
My mother-in-law decided to save me
 without hesitation.

939
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:32,960
I cried

940
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:34,520
when I heard about it.

941
00:44:37,160 --> 00:44:38,520
And I couldn't hate her anymore.

942
00:44:41,560 --> 00:44:44,640
Then, my firm got bigger and bigger.

943
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:46,640
I didn't have time or the energy

944
00:44:46,640 --> 00:44:48,120
to fixate on the past.

945
00:44:50,040 --> 00:44:51,840
You really are a person with stories.

946
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:55,240
I write stories on the internet sometimes.

947
00:44:55,560 --> 00:44:56,480
If you don't mind,

948
00:44:56,480 --> 00:44:58,280
can I write about your experience?

949
00:45:01,760 --> 00:45:04,080
Turns out that you've been chatting with me

950
00:45:04,080 --> 00:45:06,240
for writing material.

951
00:45:06,240 --> 00:45:08,400
I honestly think you've got a great story to tell.

952
00:45:08,680 --> 00:45:10,160
If it ever gets published,

953
00:45:10,160 --> 00:45:11,360
I'll cut you in on the royalty.

954
00:45:11,680 --> 00:45:12,360
No need.

955
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:14,880
I know that you writers don't make much.

956
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:16,600
The money won't do me any good.

957
00:45:17,200 --> 00:45:17,960
How about this?

958
00:45:19,240 --> 00:45:21,280
If it gets published,

959
00:45:21,280 --> 00:45:22,720
you can buy me dinner.

960
00:45:22,720 --> 00:45:23,920
That's all you want?

961
00:45:24,280 --> 00:45:25,160
How about this?

962
00:45:25,160 --> 00:45:26,440
My husband has a social tonight.

963
00:45:26,720 --> 00:45:28,080
If you're available, wait till I pick up the kids

964
00:45:28,080 --> 00:45:29,280
and we can have dinner together.

965
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:31,400
I'll buy you dinner now,

966
00:45:31,400 --> 00:45:32,760
regardless if the story gets published or not.

967
00:45:32,760 --> 00:45:34,520
I'm not being polite

968
00:45:34,520 --> 00:45:35,320
but I've got plans tonight.

969
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:36,680
I need to go back to the firm.

970
00:45:36,680 --> 00:45:38,480
Then, I need to attend this dinner.

971
00:45:38,480 --> 00:45:39,560
I need to go home to change.

972
00:45:40,200 --> 00:45:40,760
Well.

973
00:45:40,760 --> 00:45:41,800
If you're free tonight,

974
00:45:41,800 --> 00:45:43,920
you can take your kids and join us.

975
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:46,360
Maybe another time.

976
00:45:46,360 --> 00:45:48,040
The kids need to do homework.

977
00:45:48,040 --> 00:45:49,160
You know that I've got more things

978
00:45:49,160 --> 00:45:50,560
going on than you.

979
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:52,360
Okay. Keep in touch.

980
00:45:52,360 --> 00:45:53,080
Bye.

981
00:45:53,920 --> 00:45:55,160
Well, you know where I live now.

982
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:56,680
You're welcome to drop by anytime.

983
00:45:57,160 --> 00:45:58,760
It is fate that

984
00:45:58,760 --> 00:45:59,920
brought us together.

985
00:46:00,720 --> 00:46:01,840
Thank you for the washing machine.

986
00:46:01,840 --> 00:46:03,200
I will transfer the money to you later.

987
00:46:03,560 --> 00:46:04,880
Stop mentioning it!

988
00:46:06,080 --> 00:46:07,600
Bye-bye.

989
00:46:08,240 --> 00:46:09,320
Drive safe.

990
00:46:09,320 --> 00:46:10,080
Okay.
